<![CDATA[<div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-d72269bb-2f54-45f5-a235-5d2600fd501f">Thank you for your email.&nbsp;</div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-d72269bb-2f54-45f5-a235-5d2600fd501f"><br></div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-d72269bb-2f54-45f5-a235-5d2600fd501f">Your reference number for this is {!Case.CaseNumber}.</div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-e466e425-ff40-4314-8253-471a97c2aaa2"></div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-26bc3087-a898-4826-9439-468de4ae4df8"><br></div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-26bc3087-a898-4826-9439-468de4ae4df8">We will aim to respond to you as soon as possible. If you need to speak to us urgently, please call our phone line on 01242 808 740. Lines are open Monday – Friday between 8am and 5:30pm.</div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-7e892340-0142-4155-a6e9-326bd1dc429a"></div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-a7fdf329-c325-43d1-b663-737b1245dbe7"><br></div><div class="ql-block" data-block-id="block-a7fdf329-c325-43d1-b663-737b1245dbe7">Please do not reply to this email as it is an auto-generated response. We would like to thank you for your patience.&nbsp;</div>]]></td>
